data.description: Pristine in Puckett!! This wonderful four bedroom home is ready for its next owner(s). Spacious and updated, this home features a large front dining space with beautiful bay window, leading into a large living area with a bricked fireplace and ceiling beams. The kitchen has an eat-in bar with a second dining space and leads out to the spacious backyard. Off the kitchen is the fourth bedroom that is currently being used as a large office. On the other side of the living area are the other three bedrooms and two bathrooms, the master being at the end of the long hallway. All bedrooms have new carpet and are all very large. The location of this home is hard to beat. Schedule your private showing today!
